headline.main: 380 ARE DUE TODAY ON THE WEST POINT; Transport to Dock at Noon With U.S. Consular Aides From Axis Countries 19 AMBULANCE DRIVERS Diplomatic Staff Members to Get a Few Days Leave Before They Report

lead_paragraph: The Navy transport West Point, formerly the luxury liner America, was nearing New York last night at the end of her special "repatriation" voyage, on which she carried to Europe 464 ousted Axis consular officials and their families and returned with a similar group of American "official" families from Axis lands.
abstract: Consulates: U S agents due in U S on SS West Point, list
